snippet.title: Live Meditation With Gurudev | World Meditation Day 21st Dec 2024
snippet.description:
The world is coming together on the 21st of December 2024 on the occasion of World Meditation Day to meditate with Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar, this is going to be the most historic and largest meditation event. You don't want to miss out!

About #Gurudev - 
The world is coming together on the 21st of December 2024 to celebrate World Meditation Day 
World-renowned humanitarian, spiritual leader, and an ambassador of peace and human values. Through his life and work, Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar has inspired millions around the world with a vision of a stress-free and peaceful world. Gurudev founded The Art of Living, a non-profit organization that is engaged in stress-management and service initiatives across the world.

Learn Sudarshan Kriya the world's most powerful breathing technique: https://aoliv.in/learnsudarshankriya

Episode 1: क्या Daya की गलती की वजह से गई Abhijeet की बेटी की जान?
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
During a critical rescue operation, Abhijeet tragically loses his daughter Shreya due to a minor error by Daya. Three months later, a mysterious shooting incident occurs on a metro, leaving a woman injured. How will ACP Pradyuman and his team uncover the truth behind this case?

Show Name: CID Season 2 
Episode: 1
Cast: Shivaji Satam, Dayanand Shetty, Aditya Srivastava, Ansha Sayed, Ajay Nagrath, Saumya Saraswat, Narendra Gupta, Parul Rai

India's favourite crime thriller show is back! 'CID' stars Shivaji Satam, Dayanand Shetty, Aditya Srivastava and Narendra Gupta.

snippet.title: ORANGE JAM MARMALADE | Home Made Marmalade Recipe Cooking in Village | Easy Fruit Jam Recipes
snippet.description: We prepare Orange Jam Marmalade in the peaceful landscapes of our village, blending fresh oranges, sugar, and traditional cooking methods in an open-air setting. Surrounded by lush greenery and nature’s beauty, we create a sweet and tangy marmalade, perfect for spreading on fresh bread, pairing with snacks, or enhancing desserts. The natural environment adds to the charm, showcasing the simplicity and joy of village-style cooking.

Ready to shake it up with some high voltage? Presenting you Dhop Lyrical Song from Game Changer.

Game Changer is an Upcoming 2025 Movie Starring Global Star Ram Charan, Kiara Advani, Anjali, Samuthirakani, SJ Surya, Srikanth, Sunil and others. Directed by Shankar. Produced by Dil Raju, Shirish and Adityaram, under the banners Sri Venkateswara Creations and Zee Studios. Music composed by Thaman S.

GRAND RELEASE WORLDWIDE ON JANUARY 10th, 2025.

#DhopLyricalSong #GameChanger #RamCharan #KiaraAdvani #ThamanS #Shankar #DilRaju #RoshiniJKV #Prudhvi #SruthiRanjani #RamaJogayyaSastry #Dhop #DhopTeluguSong #GameChangerSongs #TeluguSongs2024

snippet.title: Best School in the World | School Aaj Kal | Take A Break
snippet.description:
What would schools say if they dropped the facade and got real? Welcome to School Aaj Kal, a hilarious yet thought-provoking comedy sketch that imagines just that! 🎓💸
In this video, we explore how schools today often focus more on profits than education, becoming money-churning machines rather than true centers of learning. From exorbitant fees and "mandatory" extracurriculars to endless add-ons like "smart classrooms" and overpriced uniforms, this sketch dives into the absurdities of modern-day schooling with a pinch of satire and a truckload of laughs.

Get ready to laugh, relate, and maybe even question the reality of today’s education system. Because sometimes, honesty is the funniest policy! 😂
#SchoolAajKal #HonestSchools #EducationSatire

Produced By - Monica Prabhudesai
Producer - Pratik Thakur
Creative Producer- Ravindra Sarowar

Writer - Nikhil Pandey
Director -  Satyam Phule
Creative Director - Sharjeel Shoeb
1st Assistant Director - Hitan Dhaktode
2nd Assistant Director - Nikhil Pandey

Costume - Ankita Sonawane 
Production Manager - Pavan Tekale
Production Asst. - Gajanan Lokhande
Runner - Nilesh Korde

Makeup- Shahin Bajwa
DOP - Akshay Jadhav, Suraj Kale

snippet.title: What Happened to Amma? അമ്മയ്ക്ക് എന്താണ് സംഭവിച്ചത്?
snippet.description:
What Happened to Amma? അമ്മയ്ക്ക് എന്താണ് സംഭവിച്ചത്? #techtraveleat #family 

As you know that I have taken a break from our journey and I am at home as my mother isn't keeping well,  I had decided not to post any videos for a while. But as many are commenting and sending messages enquiring about my mother, I thought I shall show some updates like these. Thank you so much for your support and prayers.

അമ്മയ്ക്ക് വയ്യെന്നറിഞ്ഞ് യാത്രകൾക്ക് താൽക്കാലിക വിരാമമിട്ടുകൊണ്ട് ഞാൻ നാട്ടിലെത്തിയ കാര്യം എല്ലാവരും അറിഞ്ഞുകാണുമല്ലോ. ഇതിനിടയിൽ നാട്ടിൽ നിന്നുള്ള വീഡിയോകൾ ചെയ്യേണ്ട എന്നായിരുന്നു തീരുമാനമെങ്കിലും, അമ്മയുടെ വിശേഷം തിരക്കി ധാരാളമാളുകൾ കമന്റിലും മെസ്സേജിലുമൊക്കെ വരുന്നത് കാരണമാണ് ഇങ്ങനെയൊരു വീഡിയോ ചെയ്യുവാൻ തീരുമാനിച്ചത്. നിങ്ങളുടെ സപ്പോർട്ടിനും പ്രാർത്ഥനകൾക്കും നന്ദി.

A day at a Farmhouse in Hyderabad offers a perfect blend of nature, tranquility, and authentic experiences. The city,known for its bustling urban life, is also home to several peaceful farmhouses that provide an escape into nature. Spending a day in a Hyderabad farmhouse allows you to enjoy the fresh air, lush greenery, and the calm away from the noise of the city. Whether it's enjoying traditional food,engaging in fun outdoor activities, or simply relaxing in the serene environment, Hyderabad's farmhouse cater to all. It's ideal destination for those seeking a break from the fast-paced city life and wanting to experience rural charm.

A day in the Hyderabad farmhouse offers more than just a relaxing getaway-it's an opportunity to reconnect with nature and experience the beauty of rural life. From the moment you step in, you're greeted with the refreshing sights and sounds of greenery,making it a perfect escape from the hectic city. The farmhouse often offers outdoor activities like farming,nature walks, and even games for the whole family,making it an ideal spot for group outings. In addition to the peaceful environment, the food at these farmhouses is typically made with fresh,local ingredients,providing a true taste of the region's traditional cuisine. Whether you want to enjoy a peaceful day in the lap of nature or indulge in a little adventure,Hyderabad's farmhouses provide a variety of experiences that will leave you refreshed and rejuvenated. For anyone visiting the city, a day spent at a farmhouse is truly unforgettable and worth the time.

snippet.title: OP Chautala के निधन के बाद Abhay Chautala ने दिया ये बड़ा बयान | Haryana News
snippet.description:
हरियाणा के पूर्व मुख्यमंत्री ओमप्रकाश चौटाला के निधन के बाद हरियाणा के सिरसा में मातम का माहौल। अभय सिंह चौटाला के सिरसा निवास पर लोगों के आने का सिलसिला जारी। अर्जुन चौटाला सिरसा निवास से गांव चौटाला के लिए हुए रवाना। देर शाम ओम प्रकाश चौटाला का पार्थिव शरीर देर शाम गांव चौटाला में पहुंचेगा। ओम प्रकाश चौटाला के निधन की सूचना मिलने के बाद भावुक हुए समर्थक।सुबह 8 बजे से लेकर 2 बजे तक ओम प्रकाश चौटाला का पार्थिव शरीर अंतिम दर्शनों के लिए रखा जाएगा। हरियाणा और पंजाब से कई राजनेताओं के आने की संभावना। पीएम नरेंद्र मोदी , सीएम नायब सिंह सैनी, केंद्रीय मंत्री राजनाथ सिंह , केंद्रीय मंत्री मनोहर लाल , पूर्व सीएम भूपेंद्र सिंह हुडा सहित अनेक नेताओं ने अफ़सोस जाहिर किया।

--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal and Champaklal try to convince Tappu to consider marriage, but he stands firm in his refusal. Similarly, Sonu faces pressure from her parents. How will they navigate their elders' expectations?

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Bujji Thalli Song Lyrics in Telugu

పల్లవి

గాలిలో ఊగిసలాడే దీపంలా 
ఊగిసలాడే నీ ఊసందక నా ప్రాణం
నల్లని మబ్బులు చుట్టిన చంద్రుడిలా 
చీకటి కమ్మెను నీ కబురందక నాలోకం

సుడిగాలిలో పడి పడి లేచే
పడవల్లే తడబడుతున్నా..

నీ కోసం వేచుందే నా ప్రాణం
ఓ బుజ్జితల్లి 
నా కోసం ఓ మాటైనా మాటాడే 
నా బుజ్జి తల్లి ..

 చరణం-1

నీరు లేని చేపల్లే 
తారలేని నింగల్లే 
జీవమేది నాలోన నువ్వు మాటలాడందే

మళ్ళీ యాళకొస్తానే
కాళ్ళ యేళ్ళ పడతానే 
లెంపలేసుకుంటానే
ఇంక నిన్ను యిడిపోనే
ఉప్పు నీటి ముప్పుని కూడా
గొప్పగా దాటే గట్టోణ్ణే
నీ కంటి నీటికి మాత్రం కొట్టుకుపోతానే

నీ కోసం వేచుందే
నా ప్రాణం ఓ బుజ్జితల్లి
నా కోసం ఓ మాటైనా మాటాడే
నా బుజ్జి తల్లి

చరణం-2

ఇన్నినాళ్ళ మన దూరం
తియ్యనైన ఓ విరహం 
చేదులాగ మారిందే అందిరాక నీ గారం

దేన్ని కానుకియ్యాలే
యెట్లా బుజ్జగించాలే
బెట్టు నువ్వు దించేలా లంచమేటి కావాలే

గాలివాన జాడేలేదే  రవ్వంతైనా నా చుట్టూ 
అయినా మునిగిపోతున్నానే దారే చూపెట్టు

నీ కోసం వేచుందే నా ప్రాణం
 ఓ బుజ్జితల్లి 
నా కోసం ఓ మాటైనా మాటాడే 
నా బుజ్జి తల్లి.
..............................................................................

snippet.title: मूली के पराठे में बस ये मिला दे और कमाल देखे | Mooli Paratha Recipe |Mooli ke Parathe kabitaskitchen
snippet.description:
#mooliparatharecipe #kabitaskitchen #moolirecipe 

Preparation time - 30 mins
Serving - 4 

Ingredients:

For stuffing
Mooli - 500 grams
Gram flour (besan)- 3 tbsp
Grated ginger -1 tbsp
Green chilli -1 tbsp
Turmeric powder -1/2 tsp
Chilli powder -1/2 tsp
Coriander powder -1/2 tsp
Aamchur powder - 1 tsp
Salt to taste

For dough:
Wheat flour - 2 cups
Salt -1 tsp
Water

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Episode 4256: Dunkiwala Ka Fraud
--------------------------------------------------------
When Jethalal realizes that Babu Bakkal is actually Dunkiwala, he escapes with the money, evading his men. Will he be caught?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episode No - 4256
Produced By - Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - promotes 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), a Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch all the episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:  https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZFhouqhrvP3Sx0U7qxdzJi

snippet.title: Decorating Home for Christmas Vlog in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video, join me as I transform our home into a cozy Christmas wonderland! This year, I’m mixing traditional holiday charm with creative DIY touches to make our decorations truly special. From twinkling fairy lights and garlands to homemade ornaments and festive centerpieces, you’ll find plenty of inspiration for your own holiday decor. In this video, I tried making a 2D Christmas tree on the wall and decorating it with ornaments.

#christmashomedecor #holidaydecorations #steffivlogs

From crafting unique tree ornaments to styling a festive mantelpiece, these ideas are perfect for families who love to get creative and embrace the holiday spirit. I hope this week’s vlog inspires you to deck your halls and enjoy a joyful holiday season. Don’t forget to like, comment, and subscribe for more festive fun. See you soon with another cheerful video!

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal:

Jetha calls up Babita and thanks her for the idea of setting up a fitness camp. Popatlal is not happy with the decision and asks Bhide to put this notice off the board. Upon hearing, Tapu Sena gets excited about the fitness camp.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 1329
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4273 - Sonu ki Kundli me Prem Yog!| Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi

snippet.description:
#gajarkahalwa #halwarecipe #carrothalwarecipe #cookwithparul

Preparation time - 90 minutes
Serving - 8

Ingredients : 
Carrot - 1.5 kg
Ghee -1/2 cup
Sugar - 1 cup
Cashews- 4 tbsp
Almonds - 4 tbsp
Raisins- 2 tbsp
Cardamom powder - 1/2 tsp
Mawa - 1 cup
Milk - 3 cups

snippet.title: चम्मच भर दलिया सर्दी में ऐसे खालो घुटना-कमर,जोड़ों का दर्द कभी नहीं होगा calcium भरपूर मिलेगा |DALIYA
snippet.description:
#winterrecipebyeatyammiecious 
#energyboost #daliyarecipe 

चम्मच भर दलिया सर्दी में ऐसे खालो घुटना-कमर, जोड़ों का दर्द कभी नहीं होगा calcium भरपूर मिलेगा |Dalia

Daliya ki khir aur Daliya ke Labh se Sal mein aap kabhi bhi Banakar kha sakte hain lekin Is Tarah ka Daliya jismein ki Gond bhi hai yah aap sirf sardiyon Mein Hi kha sakte hain yah aapki sehat ke liye bahut jyada Achcha Rahega to is bar aap apne diet Mein yah Daliya Gond ke sath banaa Karke Jarur se add Karen

If you want to stay Healthy then never change your lifestyle you just have to include this healthy recipes in your diet.......

Meri recipe Banane mein bahut Aasan hai aap ise Ghar per maujud Saman Se Aaram Se banaa sakte hain
रेसिपी देखने के बाद एक बार घर पर इसे ट्राई जरूर करिएगा अगर पसंद आए तो कमेंट करके जरूर बताइएगा क्या आपकी पूरी फैमिली मेंबर्स का क्या रिएक्शन रहा मुझे उम्मीद है कि सब के सब इसे जरूर पसंद करेंगे

*INGREDIENTS required :-

1/3cup - Broken Wheat
1/4cup - Edible Gum
3/4cup - Dry Coconut
3 cup - Milk
1/4cup - Dates 
1/4cup - Jaggery Powder
8-10 - Almonds
8-10 - Cashews
1-2tbs - Raisins
1ts - Dry Ginger Powder
1 pinch - Nutmeg
1/2ts - White Pepper Powder
1/2ts - Green Cardamom Powder
3-4tbs - Clarified Butter

 

            Don't forget to follow these steps:)

● LIKE  ● SHARE ● SUBSCRIBE

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

snippet.title: Sunn Mere Dil Episode 24 Teaser - 19th December 2024 - Har Pal Geo
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 24 Teaser - 19th December 2024 - Har Pal Geo

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Haseeb Hasan
Writer: Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar

Cast:

Wahaj Ali as Bilal Abdullah 
Maya Ali as Sadaf
Usama Khan as Ammar
Hira Mani as Hamsha
Amar Khan as Dania
Saba Hameed as Farzana
Syed Mohammed Ahmed as Namdaar
Shahvir Kadwani as Zaviyaar

#SunnMeraDil
#WahajAli
#MayaAli
